title: 2005 expectations
content:
It's a little bit late but we need to keep this forum a little bit alive.

So, what culture activities are you planning and what do you expect?

For me that would be:

CDs & music dvds
Judas Priest - Angel of Retribution (1 March)
System of a Down - Hypnotize and Mesmerize
Iron Maiden - Dance of death live and/or The history of IM part 2

Concerts
Megadeth & Diamond Head
Saxon
Judas Priest & The Scorpions
Graspop (with Iron Maiden)
Bospop (with Iron Maiden)

Games:
Stronghold 2

Movies:
Spongebob Squarepants

What you are hoping for
See Kiss, Black Sabbath, Ozzy Osbourne, and AC/DC live
Get myself a better guitar
learn to play proper solo's
get to Tutanchamon exposition in Germany

What you are not hoping for
To see System of a Down live.-----------------
